name: Well That's Dumb
description: Woah, Ed's going down a well because his friends Frank and Jeremy wanted him to. I mean, who wouldn't ask their friend who's small enough to fit to go down the mysterious well with no purpose sitting in the middle of nowhere? Anyways yeah slide down the wall, move the trajectory arrow with wasd and arrow keys, jump with z, space, enter, or shift, and don't touch the spike vine things.
